snippet.title: New JUDGE! For JOHNNY DEPP v Amber Heard US Trial Ft. SEC & Dr. SOUP
snippet.description:
The new judge for Johnny Depp v Amber Heard in the US trial has been announced, Penny Azcarate will now take over from Bruce White.
Join me with Les and Shelby to talk about what this could mean for Johnny Depp and Justice overall.
